window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>In an age where superhumans reign, </b><b><i>anyone</i></b><b> can end the world.</b></p> <p>Without a common enemy to unite against, humanity teeters on the brink of self-destruction. Isaac has prevented one apocalypse, but now faces a more insidious threat: humanity itself.<br> <br> Grand plans for a perfect world are crumbling, and masterplans are failing as superpowers prove to be no cure-all. Societies are shattering under pressure, pushed to their breaking points.<br> <br> With threats lurking everywhere and global power levels soaring, can Isaac and his friends keep the world from tearing itself apart without becoming the monsters they fight against?</p>"; 
